            "title": "今日申购指南及新股定位分析",
            "description": "<div class=\"rich_media_content\"><section>【今日申购指南及新股定位分析】财联社5月8日电，今日有2只新股申购，分别为创业板的<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span>太力科技</span></span></span>，沪市主板的<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span>威高血净</span></span></span>；无新股上市。</section></div>",
